snippet.title: Morphman gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Morphman, Dos PC game produced by Dynamic Dimensions Development in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/morphman/16984/
MorphMan is a very interesting science fiction game, well done, with graphics quite successful and very advanced idea although the game is made in the early 90's.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
